PROJECT.NAME: heTriNodu1-mito
PROJECT.TITLE: Triaenophorus nodulosus, mitochondrial assembly, heTriNodu1-mito.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project collects the mitochondrial assembly of Triaenophorus nodulosus. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).

PROJECT.NAME: heTriNodu1-haploid
PROJECT.TITLE: Triaenophorus nodulosus, genome assembly, heTriNodu1-haploid, alternate haplotype.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project provides an alternate haplotype genome assembly of Triaenophorus nodulosus. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
